  			<p>Donny Shaw is the Outreach Coordinator for PPF and the Lead Blogger & Researcher of OpenCongress. Since our launch in 2007, he has been digging through legislative texts, monitoring roll call votes, tracking bills and adding editorial context to congressional info in order to make it intelligible for non-DC-insiders. He lives in Western Massachusetts, and when he's not researching Congress he's taking care of apple trees and picking berries.</p>
